      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and serves as a reliable transportation option for those on a budget. The exterior displays several noticeable scratches and some paint fading consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin shows moderate wear and tear on the upholstery, though all essential electronics and controls remain operational. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles adequately for daily commuting, though it lacks the refinement of a newer model. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a practical vehicle that prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
