    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs great, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It's got plenty of life left in it and is ready for some new adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019ll love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
